OOC: Sorry

Menasor notices his target getting up and leaving, he stops his climb into
the air, and halts for a moment, 600 feet high in the air. He aims his huge
Cyclone gun at Firearm. The huge barrel of the blaster locks onto the
target, and fires a huge torent of energy. Then after his shot, Menasor
plunges downwards, at a huge speed, heading straight for the ground. I he
cant rid himself of his opponents, he will crash them.
